data.description: This beautifully and well cared for residence sits on over a quarter acre lot in the highly desired Redbird Ranch Community. The single story home boasts a 3 car garage, and inviting landscaping with mature trees and stone flower beds in front. As you enter the home you are greeted with flexible living space perfect for a play area, home gym, or separate dining room. The bright open floor plan continues to an island kitchen with ample cabinet space, upgraded granite counter tops, built in stainless steel oven and gas cooking. The main living area features a cozy stone fireplace and additional dining area. The primary bedroom offers an abundance of natural light from the large bay window. The primary bathroom is complete with a double vanity, garden tub, and separate shower. The backyard is the focal point of this home with an oversized extended deck and beautiful outdoor stone fireplace! With mature trees and expansive yard this home is its only little oasis just minutes for shopping, dining, and so much more. New Roof in 2021 with 40 year transferrable warranty
